latestPosts.caption:
Why are so many young Indians still struggling to find meaningful work, even after completing skill training?

In the first episode of The Skill Edit,  we bring together leaders who are not just asking the hard questions — but working on the ground to close the gap.

Featuring Anita Rajan (Advisor, Tata STRIVE), Sougata Roy Choudhury (Executive Director, CII), and Dr. Gayathri Vasudevan (Chief Impact Officer, Sambhav Foundation), and moderated by Aparna Bansal from Josh Talks — this conversation sets the stage for what skilling in India must become: inclusive, responsive, and future-ready.

Full episode drops tomorrow, Stay Tuned!
. 
. 
#joshtalks #skillingindia #futureofwork #jobsforyouth #upskill #skillsthatmatter #realimpact #empoweryouth #careertalks #newindia
